{"blogid": "126593268", "writerAge": "码龄2年", "writerBlogNum": "82", "writerCollect": "23", "writerComment": "21", "writerFan": "12", "writerGrade": "4级", "writerIntegral": "976", "writerName": "激进的土豆", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_126593268.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "21188", "writerRankWeekly": "1703", "writerThumb": "124", "writerVisitNum": "8388", "blog_read_count": "277", "blog_time": "于 2022-08-29 22:18:43 发布", "blog_title": "IDEA整合tomcat教程", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<h1><strong>首先创建一个普通的Java工程：</strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\a715834302e44188a66ab5e37e325ccd.png\"/></p>\n<h1>右键项目找到project structure(快捷键：Ctrl+Alt+Shift+S)</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\3854fd62859a4e6fb05cd73f74d1ace5.png\"/></p>\n<h1>点击Moduls,点击+号，选择web,点击OK</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\c5087c8f846945f88bf4487eee9f3edf.png\"/></p>\n<h1>这样就会在工程里生成web模块里面有个WEB-INF里有我们最重要的web.xml,必须的有这个模块</h1>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\69104436b40e4f998f53be2d4158aea6.png\"/></p>\n<h1>点击在idea运行处的Edit Configurations</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\cc92b6917e6a442cbffa211e7665f7da.png\"/></p>\n<h1>点击+号，找到tomcat server下的local(本地),ps:不要选择TomEE server</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\aa93249f5a6a4973a5409635545e048c.png\"/></p>\n<h1>点击右侧的Configure,配置Tomcat的本地路径。路径到Tomcat的根目录就可以</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\1bbc5ce6de7d4564a1db57eecbe02928.png\"/></p>\n<h1>之后再点回project structure（↑的步骤有位置，这里不放图片了），点击Artifacts,点击+号，选择 web Application Exploded: From Modules...点击OK</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\b12d1e8fa14b4fa087f52c37fe2e617e.png\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"> <img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\92941a971c6e46ac8d536432bf71c4bd.png\"/></p>\n<h1>修改output directory路径为你自己安装的tomcat下的webapps，点击OK</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\4b8d95975bdf402db08c750db1e1080b.png\"/></p>\n<h1>点击idea运行处的Edit Configurations，点击Deployment选项卡，点击+号，选择Artifact，自动添加了。</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\4a9f2bfac6c144edacf7f26ce8aebf47.png\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\37e46ef6857e4bddac873dc34be5574c.png\"/></p>\n<p>会出现这个： </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\2a9e97d0dc2e4557bf94c29a28b217d4.png\"/></p>\n<h1>回到Server选项卡，可以修改端口号以及服务器的两个配置改为update classes and resources。</h1>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\c923da9324b54b148b884c92f6252031.png\"/></p>\n<h1>在web目录下新建HTML文件，点击启动服务器，可以通过（自己修改的地址）<code>http://localhost:8080/javaWeb/index.html</code>地址来访问自己的项目。</h1>\n</div>\n</div>"}